title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jan 18 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jan 18 2022
description:
Why the left already can't stand the Youngkin administration. Joy Reid very down on Youngkin. Clay ponders what he says he's thought many times: Is it an act with Joy Reid, a character she's playing, or is she really as uninformed and unintelligent as she seems? What was the dumbest covid decision? C&B give inspired lists! Judicial Watch’s Tom Fitton joins Clay and Buck to discuss the Jan. 6th and Fauci probes. Stephen Colbert: Abolish the senate.
